Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Ahh… the hot water felt so nice…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:11.68,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for using your bath before you…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:15.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Oh?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.62,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this Hasunosora-san?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.94,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don’t need the “-san”?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.90,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Yugiri Tsuzuri.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.43,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It’s raining hard, so I’m at my house.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:35.43,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Kozu…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.20,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Otomune Kozue is here as well.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:41.31,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Is she doing what I think she is…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.70,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Diligently calling to inform the school…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:48.71,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yes, understood.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.69,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,By tomorrow morning…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.39,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What time?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.75,0:01:00.22,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Return by 8:00, okay.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.80,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Okay then, seeya.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,“Seeya”…!?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:11.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kozu. Are you finished?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:14.91,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am. Thank you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.91,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I feel much warmer now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:20.78,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But you know I would have been fine going after you, right?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:25.10,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Nah, there was something I had to do.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.26,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Just now?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:29.41,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:32.50,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You have to call the dorms if you’re not coming back before curfew.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:33.90,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Did you know that?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:37.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Of course I knew that, but…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.85,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You called in for me, too.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.99,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’ve become a hard worker.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Right…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You really have.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.87,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Because I couldn’t say anything to you back then.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.26,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What are you–?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.27,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’ve become an upperclassman now.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:05.64,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s right…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:11.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You’re exactly right. We really have.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:17.71,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Listen, I’d feel guilty if you caught a cold.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.31,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and take your bath now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:21.16,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Aw…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:27.52,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But I always dreamed of sharing the bath at my house with one of my friends.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.11,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn’t have told me to go ahead!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Mission failed.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.39,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kaho-san…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.22,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It looks like you had the right idea after all.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:52.84,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,To think that this would happen again…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Are those two alright…?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.04,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just got a message!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:16.72,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What did Otomune-senpai tell you!?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hang on. Hang on–\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:25.56,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hang on… Wait, I said!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.91,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I understand that you’re worried, but still!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:33.09,Kaho,,0,0,0,,“We will be staying the night at Tsuzuri’s house.”\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That’s a relief…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:46.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I was so worried they’d force themselves to get back here even through all this heavy rain…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:50.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What, go all that way?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,There’s no way they would do that…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,They wouldn’t, right?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.83,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Ahaha… but see?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:01.16,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She’s still with Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.90,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That’s right, but…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.01,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry about it.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I have younger sisters, so I know what it’s like.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:18.73,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,N-No, I can’t always be taking advantage of your hospitality.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.52,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I mean, I wouldn’t say “always”...\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Actually, usually I’m that one that’s–\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:34.27,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s only thanks to your suggestion that they’re together, or that we’ll be performing as a full group, you know?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:40.94,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess, but wasn’t it your idea to send them to help out with the food stall?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That was only because I happened to meet Reika-san earlier…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And besides.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it really turned out okay. It’s raining so hard…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I-It’s not like the rain automatically means it went wrong!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:03.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You know, it might even be a good thing! They ended up staying the night together at Tsuzuri-senpai’s house, right?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Alright, I’ll try to think of it that way.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.86,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,There are still things we have to do, after all.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.91,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let’s keep doing what we can for those two!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:20.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.71,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s do our best to perform as a full group!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:26.71,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Right!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:32.19,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So right now, we don’t need to worry about them! They’ll be fine!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:33.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Right…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:36.97,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Right?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.07,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s do this!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.89,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Go, go, let’s go–!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Sayaka-chan?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…I just remembered.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:53.44,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I didn’t wake her up yesterday or the day before yesterday.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:02.17,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I didn’t make her lunch, and I didn’t walk her to and from school.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So that should mean she’ll be fine without me, right!?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:09.44,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does this mean I no longer have to worry about her?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:12.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Or am I just skirting my responsibility to her?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:18.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Wait, shouldn’t I be going to her right now, even though it’s raining?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.35,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.01,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chaaaan!!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.18,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You asleep?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Why are you even asking?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This is the fourth time now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.22,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Just wondering.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I’m asleep.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.71,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,If you really were asleep, you wouldn’t say you were…!\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.79,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,There was something I wanted to say…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:06.36,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’ve been trying to tell you, but it feels like someone’s stealing the words before they leave my mouth.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.41,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It’s been like this for a while now.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.62,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Today was really fun, huh?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.16,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Huh, did you fall asleep?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:26.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,There’s no way I could after you said you wanted to tell me something.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:32.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I had fun today, yes.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.47,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Um…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.86,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…I’m doing my best, too.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.27,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Tsuzuri?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:52.40,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…I don’t mean that you shouldn’t do your best.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:59.24,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I didn’t say this because I didn’t want to make you feel bad,\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.98,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,but… um…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.59,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m also doing my best.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.94,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So you shouldn’t feel like you need to do everything.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:14.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Does it look like I’m overworking myself?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:16.58,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.44,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,That’s not what I mean.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:24.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I just want to support you…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:29.00,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So I will. That’s what I wanted to say.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:32.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Alright.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Whoa–\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.84,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…You move a lot in your sleep.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.88,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m not actually asleep.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…I’m glad I finally said it.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:50.65,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What you just said?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:52.74,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.85,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’ve always wanted to tell you.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.01,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So I’m glad I did.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:10.69,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I’m glad you told me, too.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.73,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Hey, Kozu.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.83,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You’re not hiding something, are you?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Why do you ask?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:30.92,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You don’t really say what you think.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.36,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Usually, I have to ask.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:38.89,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:45.39,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Recently, you haven’t really talked much about Love Live! either.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Really?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.27,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I guess so.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.56,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Then–\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
